import React, { Component } from 'react'; import { DateTime } from 'luxon'; class UserSlideMakeup extends Component { render() { const { activeUser } = this.props; if (!activeUser) return null; const { name, picture, login, phone, email, registered, location, uniqueID, clickOnCard } = activeUser; const registeredFixed = DateTime.fromISO(registered.date); return (
Personal info
Name: {name.first} {name.last}
Username: {login.username}
Password: {login.password}
Registered: {registeredFixed.toFormat('yyyy-MM-dd')}
Contacts
Phone: {phone}
Email: {email}
Location
Country: {location.country}
State: {location.state}
City: {location.city}
Street: {location.street.name} {location.street.number}
) }; }; export default UserSlideMakeup;
